profile:
Solid Build Interiors Inc is a unique family run contracting company with an overall experience of 35 years in the industry. Communication is our key focus in providing high quality work in making our valued customers ideas come to life. step by step walk throughs are offered to help provide expertise and knowledge in design for our customers. We in, Solid Build Interiors Inc, believe that quality of work should be provided no matter the magnitude of the task. Expertise in bathroom remodelling, basement renovations, and as well as kitchen makeover, provided with licensed electrician and plumber. We hope you choose us to help you with your next big remodelling mission.  


Please call, 647-830-9649. For a visit to organize a free quote. We canâ€™t wait to hear your amazing ideas.
